Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.79,0:01:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(275,387)}小翼和我...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(422,387)}不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你和我根本就不是双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你根本就不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:01:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想一直都和小翼在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我特别喜欢小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是像小翼喜欢翔那样地非常地喜欢小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我虽然可能成不了小翼的翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过只要小翼能够恢复精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小翼要是死了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样忧郁的死了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能也会伤心的死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说小翼就是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论什么时候都会在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能永远在我身边么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的全都雪白一片了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的雪下得好大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚搬来这里的那天也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前大家都写信给翔同学了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的父母给大家写了回信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在老师就给大家念一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给4年2班的各位同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家的来信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读了大家一封封的来信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔在学校的样子一个个清清楚楚地浮现在我们的眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在那中间有着太多的我们所不知道的翔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这着实让我们很吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经很清楚的感受到了各位同学对翔的喜爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常感谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们把各位的来信都带到了翔的墓前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一封封的念给了翔听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在翔一定在天国一边笑着一边回想着大家的模样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(269,387)}回想起来翔真的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:05:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(524,387)}翔 已经过了2个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有了翔大家都很伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾经不知道怎么办才好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在已经不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有小光在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后也会和小光一直在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...4年2班的各位同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望可以把各位同学的来信...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陨石？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 听说以前这一带曾经有陨石坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你说的是在茨城牧场后面的山上落下的那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有半年的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有人报告说有类似陨石样的东西坠落下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们去确认时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没有发现任何象陨石的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:06:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那一带有没有什么草木枯萎的现象呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有特别注意过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个和陨石有什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 倒不一定有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茨城牧场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼 一起去理科室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要做值日呢 你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们先去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:07:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来每一分钟量一次温度并且观察水的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后带水沸腾后稍等一会儿记录温度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温度上升一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,21度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,21度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荻原 现在几度了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,22度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,22度 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 23度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是几度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道 它不停呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 说清楚点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你来看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 温度上升了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,42度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在这一带啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确好像什么都没有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果什么也没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果假设不是陨石的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然有那么多的报道就应该有什么事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有地震以外的记录的话就可能会有些线索了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地磁气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试着按照你的建议作的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它会根据你的神经脉冲自动产生出防护盾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小还可以改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的性质根卡利恩刀一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用反卡利恩粒子做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之这个程度是目前能达到的最大的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个能用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它消耗的能量特别大所以要小心使用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对于近身战来说这可能已经是极限能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 要是有中距离作战的武器就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在准备呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是种能大量装载卡利恩炮弹的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:10:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要继续探测地底的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能让她们两个来一次这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得必须把今后的事件好好跟她们说说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再有像上次那样临时拒绝出战的事我们就很难办了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我觉得有必要让她们掌握整个事件的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 睡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能过去你那里睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪开闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种感觉 小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 再慢点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的鞋带断了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼 你等一会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去换新的鞋带
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 小光 我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦 我很快就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼 来这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起滑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的吧 你刚才不是滑的很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼体育一向都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习一下很快就会熟练的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 一起滑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一会儿就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 再练一会就能和大家一起滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玛基出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:15:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们回去的时候先去奥林蒂娜一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 只是说说话而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许你们二位已经有所了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的玛基和以前负责收集数据的那头五只玛基的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗能力已经有很大的不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那之后第六只开始每只都在不断的在进化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们的战斗能力明显地在提高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是它们并不是简单地变得更凶暴而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来玛基就具有毁灭生物体基本构造的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而从第六只以后的被我们称为母体玛基
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.11,0:15:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生出来的玛基们的能力变得更强了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个散播气体状粒子的能力也是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有一只玛基存在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它周围的生物就会大量的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前为止进化的玛基们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后仍将进化的玛基们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须由我们来负责消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我们打算使用所有我们能用的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在开发卡利恩和反卡利恩的各种武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把FIGURE的战斗能力发挥到极限
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然玛基这么危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向本星请求救援不是更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使现在向本星求援也已经迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥利蒂娜 这个事...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在再隐瞒这事已经没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是两天前得到的结论
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最初的五只出现的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这些是第六只开始以后出现的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛基们的活动区域明显地扩大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由本星的玛基研究数据
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这个星球的进化数据结合之后模拟演算的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在放任不管的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛基的增生将以几何级数扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个星球的生物将毁灭殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这个期限是三个月之内
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个月？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这只是个模拟演算不过可能性非常的高
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底这原本是我的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却给你们二人添了那么多麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是已经没有犹豫的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 小光不需要道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小光在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信小光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:18:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得她们很可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这也是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥林蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还说这个干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不应该把那么小的孩子也卷进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼和小光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说哪个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说“没有犹豫的时间”的可是你自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有堆积如山的事得干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这事我也有责任的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:19:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼 就是这么滑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 危险不危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 一会儿就好 我们一起滑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 青山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我去集合队员 你等着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走啦 小光 回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢啦 多亏你帮忙 茨原
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没打算帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 一个个吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实新先生表扬我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我搓面团的方法很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烘烤也很到位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 爸爸真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也多亏了你们的帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 你们明天不上学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午我们去哪里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定买这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要买这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 选好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很衬你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.33,0:22:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.38,0:22:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小翼 别老跟着我买啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.42,0:22:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.34,0:22:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 我想要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.43,0:22:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.69,0:22:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.52,0:22:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.61,0:22:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.07,0:22:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.74,0:22:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.53,0:22:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.83,0:22:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走路要好好看着前面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.97,0:23:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.22,0:23:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.79,0:23:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是有这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这几个月来有好多次观测到能看到局部的地磁气的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.42,0:23:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具体是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.30,0:23:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地磁气具有短周期变化的脉动特性
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.60,0:23:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,测量值就像图上这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.18,0:24:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在特定的地方有瞬间的异常变动
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.32,0:24:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般而言短周期的变化多数
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.49,0:24:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由于太阳活动的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.91,0:24:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这些变化比太阳活动的影响更为迅速周期更短
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.29,0:24:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是由地震或者火山活动引起的变化的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.33,0:24:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能够很自然地被观测到阶段性的波段变化
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.63,0:24:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这些却没有这个现象
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.38,0:24:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么可以假设为哪些原因呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.55,0:24:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始我认为很有可能是设备的故障收集到了些杂音
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.10,0:24:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看来不太象
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.06,0:24:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还在调查中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.65,0:24:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有没有类似的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.15,0:24:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这样的事以前从来没有过
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.37,0:24:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.67,0:25:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒 很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.01,0:25:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼已经滑的很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.26,0:25:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就自己滑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.97,0:25:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我还是很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.64,0:25:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.89,0:25:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你要摔跤的话我会扶助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.52,0:25:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.52,0:25:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.40,0:25:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.15,0:25:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽情地滑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.61,0:25:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.99,0:25:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看呀 大家都很支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.16,0:25:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.49,0:25:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.37,0:25:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一下下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.56,0:26:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.10,0:26:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.03,0:26:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.07,0:26:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.74,0:26:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿杖敲人是犯规的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.49,0:26:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.03,0:26:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己撞上来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.99,0:26:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.21,0:26:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些男生又要打架了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.75,0:26:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.21,0:26:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你们故意追上来绊我们的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.13,0:26:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.96,0:26:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们的做法太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.47,0:26:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.72,0:26:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们自己太笨了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.89,0:26:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.23,0:26:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.57,0:26:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.73,0:26:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都住手
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.20,0:27:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都住手
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.25,0:27:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.21,0:27:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛 打架可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.88,0:27:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.51,0:27:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.34,0:27:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先放
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.30,0:27:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了 今天不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.43,0:27:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.81,0:27:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.06,0:27:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.27,0:27:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.19,0:27:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.82,0:27:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午休的时候真是吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.66,0:27:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是阻止茨原他们的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.95,0:27:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我自己也吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.12,0:27:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉就出声了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.13,0:27:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.67,0:27:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼居然可以这样说话
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.01,0:28:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有小光在我身边呀
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.97,0:28:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.93,0:28:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.14,0:28:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正要去飞鸟家玩
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.73,0:28:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.52,0:28:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼 去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.07,0:28:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 小光也去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.05,0:28:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.09,0:28:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.47,0:28:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.97,0:28:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.43,0:28:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都好精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.97,0:28:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞鸟也该学学嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.35,0:28:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.73,0:28:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈快点出去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.81,0:28:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.23,0:28:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家慢慢玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.98,0:29:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.15,0:29:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞鸟的妈妈真温柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.82,0:29:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你们不了解她的真面目罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.53,0:29:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.54,0:29:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.66,0:29:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时在家总是爱说“那个做了吗”
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.54,0:29:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“这个不可以做”什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.75,0:29:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.67,0:29:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 和我妈妈一样
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.50,0:29:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看电视的时候总会说
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.00,0:29:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“不要看那种东西了 快点学习”
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.72,0:29:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常回想要是没有妈妈在就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.18,0:29:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.72,0:29:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.76,0:29:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我倒觉得有这么一个人在身边的话也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.99,0:30:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥林蒂娜 玛基出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.49,0:30:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 快点联系她们
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.53,0:30:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.29,0:30:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玛基吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.08,0:30:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.67,0:30:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.71,0:30:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有小光会和我一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.64,0:31:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.05,0:32:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中继能量转换器发射
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.76,0:32:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀和盾的能量都不足
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.85,0:32:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.98,0:33:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥林蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.73,0:33:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人又从下方攻击来了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.34,0:33:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是强力溶解液
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.92,0:33:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还有这招
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.68,0:33:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量全部耗尽
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.04,0:34:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼 要上咯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.50,0:34:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.88,0:34:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不能补充能量
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.14,0:34:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多小心
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.97,0:34:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.53,0:34:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 靠近不了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.62,0:34:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张着盾 从玛基上方跳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.83,0:34:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用盾保护身体同时用刀刺
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.00,0:34:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.33,0:34:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.75,0:34:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.11,0:35:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼 不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.57,0:35:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀的能量要不够了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.82,0:35:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀已经被夺走了 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.03,0:35:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有靠我们自己的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.83,0:35:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.99,0:35:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.08,0:36:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼 不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.67,0:36:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.13,0:36:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.09,0:36:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 感觉好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.72,0:36:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小光你怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.64,0:36:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.85,0:36:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有小翼在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.47,0:36:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.60,0:36:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.52,0:36:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会保护好你的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.40,0:36:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.36,0:36:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光能办到的我也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.90,0:37:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.16,0:38:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.29,0:38:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.13,0:38:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.47,0:38:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.09,0:38:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.26,0:38:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.01,0:38:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.85,0:38:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.07,0:38:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.36,0:38:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光有好好地在睡觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.49,0:38:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.49,0:38:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.08,0:38:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气很冷你也多小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.83,0:38:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.00,0:39:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 我今天可以不去学校在家照顾小光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.59,0:39:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.55,0:39:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸会偶尔去看小光的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.26,0:39:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翼好好去学校上课
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.22,0:39:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.77,0:39:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.48,0:39:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 走好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.65,0:39:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.03,0:39:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.99,0:39:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.41,0:39:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是我真的太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.34,0:40:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是反卡利恩弹药吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.51,0:40:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.72,0:40:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由大量的反卡利恩粒子组成的坚硬外壳
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.35,0:40:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内部充填了扩散性的卡利恩粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.81,0:40:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有现在也不需要担心往刀和盾提供能量了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.78,0:40:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从卫星轨道投射的大输出量
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.24,0:40:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以覆盖大范围了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.66,0:40:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不再需要中继转换装置了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.91,0:40:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些就是我们现在能做的所有的努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.13,0:41:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来啦 小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.43,0:41:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.26,0:41:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 完全康复
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.02,0:41:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.52,0:41:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着天丸去散步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.35,0:41:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.38,0:41:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.68,0:41:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉身体还是不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.22,0:42:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 只是发了一下呆
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.27,0:42:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是应该好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.23,0:42:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.94,0:42:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.96,0:42:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然枯萎的区域和这数据
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.71,0:42:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.60,0:42:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.37,0:43:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都装备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.24,0:43:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.45,0:43:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿这些弹药能够发挥预测的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.58,0:43:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.72,0:43:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 都这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.51,0:43:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想请你们帮忙调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.89,0:43:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我的身体有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.14,0:45:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终有一天必须和小翼分开的小光
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.15,0:45:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和小光在一起就什么都不怕的小翼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.69,0:45:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲密无间的两人终于走到了那无法回避的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.49,0:45:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 你在回避我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.70,0:45:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 没那回事儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.04,0:45:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于 母体玛基的藏身之所被发现了
